Package: opsrdev
Type: Package
Title: Access Patent Data with the European Patent Office "Open Patent Services" (OPS) API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paul Oldham
Maintainer: Paul Oldham <poldham@mac.com>
Description: The European Patent Office Open Patent Services (OPS) provides
    free access to millions of patent records. opsr provides basic functions for authenticating, retrieving
    and parsing JSON formatted patent data from OPS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
